00:36:38,740 --> 00:36:40,617
Refais plus jamais ça.

581
00:36:43,328 --> 00:36:44,412
Lâche-moi, putain.

582
00:36:44,496 --> 00:36:46,373
Tire-toi !

583
00:36:47,582 --> 00:36:48,959
Tire-toi.

584
00:36:49,042 --> 00:36:50,043
Putain !

