Les filles, descendez.

607
00:38:44,574 --> 00:38:46,034
Hé, mec !

608
00:38:49,120 --> 00:38:49,954
Debout !

609
00:39:12,602 --> 00:39:13,728
Julius !

610
00:39:22,946 --> 00:39:24,114
T'avais raison.

611
00:39:24,197 --> 00:39:25,240
